<p>Sometimes no matter what we do, we’ll be faced with an unexpected issue. Whether it is a grievance, disciplinary, long-term sick case or receipt of an Employment Tribunal claim (ET1), we can help. Call us; we’ll go through the issue with you, discuss your options and then act as necessary.</p>
<p>In terms of rules and regulations, our services revolve primarily around employment law advice, the creation of contracts of employment and the provision of employee handbooks / manuals.</p></td>
